{
  "chapter": 87,
  "chapter_summary": "第八十七回 血洗一身孽。龙啸云为求死前往金钱帮总舵，欲将怜花宝典献给上官金虹。他踏上石阶即被十八名黄衣人围住，对方根本不让他进院一步。龙啸云自报家门后，对方确认其身份，随即一刀两剑判官笔齐发，龙啸云当场被杀，喉管刺穿，死不瞑目。用油纸包着的怜花宝典随之被血染红，无人理会，从此绝传。与此同时，阿飞在路旁竹林削竹为剑，准备对抗上官金虹。孙小红在旁静观，对竹剑能否对付上官金虹表示怀疑。本章以龙啸云之死揭示上官金虹的铁腕统治，也暗示阿飞即将踏上决战之路。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来金钱帮的总舵果然在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 87,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qian_bang_shu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "金钱帮属下",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "你是谁？来干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 87,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "找人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 87,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qian_bang_shu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "金钱帮属下",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "找谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 87,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们的帮主上官金虹是不是已回来了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 87,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qian_bang_shu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "金钱帮属下",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "帮主已回来了，请问足下……",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 87,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我要见他，有样东西想送给他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 87,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qian_bang_shu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "金钱帮属下",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "请稍候，帮主现在不见客。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 87,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他是不是还和李寻欢在里面？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 87,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qian_bang_shu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "金钱帮属下",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 87,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么我现在就要见他。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 87,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qian_bang_shu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "金钱帮属下",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "请问尊姓大名？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 87,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姓龙，我有样极重要的东西现在非交给他不可，你们若是耽误了大事，这责任谁能担当得起？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 87,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qian_bang_shu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "金钱帮属下",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "姓龙……前两天要和帮主结拜的，莫非就是你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 87,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 87,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们这是干什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 87,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "用这样的剑也能对付上官金虹？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 87,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 147
    }
  ],
